cond edition only), as Salinas' rediscovery of the piece came too late. The piece is not mentioned in I.L.Palermo and so is seemingly no longer in the museum.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":233,"html":234},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> VIII 697 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002649\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002649\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] 238 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7318\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Salinas NSA 1883 567 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":236,"html":237},"handnote"," Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":239,"html":240},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  ",[242,244,247,248],{"html":243},"Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag",{"id":245,"lang":109,"html":246},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\" style=\"left: -4em;\">Col. 1\u003Cbr>\u003C/span>  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Marcus · Sicribonius\n                    Marci  libertus ·\n                    Stymphalus\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Marcus\">M(arcus)\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nom